(2, NULL, '2', 'GLOBAL', 'Community Involvement', 'It is the number of participatory planning or public engagement activities that have been organized in each LL.', 'custom_unit', 'number of activities organized', 'These activities may not be necessarily organized by the SUM project. LLs should provide a list with the events that have been organized. The engagement of the community in each event needs to be comprehensively explained', 1, 0, NULL, NOW(), NOW()),
